name: Atenciones por distrito
query:
SELECT 
    e.distrito AS "Distrito:Data:150",
    COUNT(a.name) AS "Cantidad de Atenciones:Int:150"
FROM 
    `tabMascota` m
JOIN 
    `tabAtencion` a ON a.parent = m.name
JOIN 
    `tabEfector` e ON a.efector = e.name
GROUP BY 
    e.distrito
ORDER BY 
    COUNT(a.name) DESC
